{"arkId":"cl010113455","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113455","modified ":"2025-10-31","title":"Coffret, d\u0027une paire avec OA 12169 1","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Coffret, d\u0027une paire avec OA 12169 1"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1819 - 1827","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 560 - Claude Ott, Acc\u00e8s r\u00e9serv\u00e9","room":"Salle 560, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1819,"endYear":1827,"imprecision":"","text":"1er tiers du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Odiot, Jean-Baptiste-Claude","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"08\/06\/1763","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"23\/05\/1850","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3176320"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12169 2","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; coffret","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Coffret d\u0027une paire. Les deux coffrets rectangulaires sont port\u00e9s chacun par quatre pieds toupies. Chaque face est cantonn\u00e9e par deux pilastres corinthiens. Sur les longs c\u00f4t\u00e9s, deux amours en buste s\u2019achevant en feuilles d\u2019acanthe et se prolongeant en rinceaux tiennent une couronne autour d\u2019un monogramme. Ces amours sont inspir\u00e9s d\u2019un motif antique des bains de Titus, grav\u00e9 par Carletti en 1776. Les petits c\u00f4t\u00e9s sont orn\u00e9s d\u2019un d\u00e9cor d\u2019arabesques, incluant des thyrses, des couronnes, des rubans, des oiseaux, des papillons et des bijoux (diad\u00e8mes et colliers). \r\nSur le couvercle du coffret, un amour cueille un fruit. Le couvercle est orn\u00e9 en outre d\u2019un d\u00e9cor appliqu\u00e9 de rinceaux, de t\u00eates de femmes et de thyrses agr\u00e9ment\u00e9s de couronnes, de rubans et d\u2019oiseaux.\r\n\r\nLe mod\u00e8le d\u00e9rive des coffrets en lapis et vermeil de la toilette disparue, offerte par la Ville de Paris \u00e0 l\u0027imp\u00e9ratrice Marie-Louise, lors de son mariage avec Napol\u00e9on en 1810.  L\u0027ex\u00e9cution avait \u00e9t\u00e9 confi\u00e9e au bronzier Thomire et \u00e0 l\u0027orf\u00e8vre Odiot, qui en r\u00e9p\u00e8te ici le mod\u00e8le. Le peintre Prud\u0027hon avait donn\u00e9 un dessin pour les amours jardiniers. Le reste du d\u00e9cor revient sans doute \u00e0 l\u0027ornemaniste Adrien-Louis-Marie Cavelier (1785-1867).","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"21,5","displayDimension":"21,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"27,2","displayDimension":"27,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"20,3","displayDimension":"20,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Legs Audrey B. Love, par l\u0027interm\u00e9diaire de Foundation for French Museums, 2005","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Love, Audrey B.","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du conseil","value":"26\/01\/2005","startYear":2005,"endYear":2005},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e